('59cf179e-bfea-43dc-9df8-d7aeea05f105', 'paul-ricard', 'Paul Ricard', 'MachiningCloud / DP Technology / Hexagon Manufacturing Intelligence', 'Founder & President, MachiningCloud; Co-founder & President, DP Technology (ESPRIT CAM)', NULL, 'https://espritcam.hexagon.com', 'Manufacturing Software Builders', 'Founder & President of MachiningCloud, the cloud-based tooling data platform revolutionizing how CNC shops access cutting tool information. Previously co-founded DP Technology and built ESPRIT CAM into a global standard for multi-axis CNC programming before its acquisition by Hexagon Manufacturing Intelligence. Has shaped digital manufacturing across two generations — from CAM software to cloud-native tooling intelligence.', 'Co-founded DP Technology in 1982 and grew ESPRIT into a category-defining multi-axis CAM platform — edit-free G-code, deep post support, and adoption across mill, turn, mill-turn, Swiss, wire EDM, and additive. DP Technology was acquired by Hexagon Manufacturing Intelligence in 2021.', '["https://www.amtonline.org/article/la-bonne-vie-40-years-and-going-strong","https://espritcam.hexagon.com/webinar/get-to-know-dp-technology-in-a-webinar-hosted-by-co-founder-paul-ricard","http://espritcam.com/company/about"]'::jsonb, 27, NULL, 18, 15, 15, 11, 7, 7, '2026', 'published', '2026-06-04T17:36:17.983793+00:00', 'editorial', 'editorial@jobline.ai', 'JobLine Editorial', true),
